BALDWIN
v.
UNIV. OF CINCINNATI HOSP. MED. CTR. 2018-0839 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

Miscellaneous case. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion to amend complaint denied as moot. O'Connor, C.J., and Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur. O'Donnell, Kennedy, and French, JJ., concur in granting respondent's motion to dismiss but would also grant relator's motion to amend complaint.
